tasks.instruction: Create a product requirement document (PRD) for the 'DelegateMUN' website, including detailed content requirements, dark mode design, animations, and navigation planes for the documentation page.
Design the software architecture for the 'DelegateMUN' website, ensuring it supports dark mode, animations, and navigation planes for the documentation page.

Develop the 'DelegateMUN' website using React, JavaScript, and Tailwind CSS. Ensure the website includes a main page, individual pages for all main contents, and a documentation page with navigation planes. Implement dark mode and add as many animations as possible.
